boofcv.factory.fiducial

Class FactoryFiducialCalibration

  • java.lang.Object
    • boofcv.factory.fiducial.FactoryFiducialCalibration

  • public class FactoryFiducialCalibration
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates detectors of calibration targets. These detectors return found key points in the image and their known 2D location on the fiducial.
